        <div class="container lp__section">
            <h3 class="lp__headline mb-5">FAQ</h3>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6 col-12">
                    <p>Below you’ll find some of the frequently asked questions. If you still need help, feel free to
                        reach us using the link at the bottom of the page.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lp__faq__wrapper">
                <div class="lp__faq">
                    <div class="lp__faq__headline" onclick="window.toggleFaq(this)"><svg width="20" height="20"
                            viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd"
                                d="M20 11.4286H11.4286V20H8.57143V11.4286H0V8.57143H8.57143V0H11.4286V8.57143H20V11.4286Z" />
                        </svg>
                        <h3>What is SOLANA?</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="lp__faq__content">
                        <p>Solana is a blockchain network that seeks to develop an ecosystem of cryptocurrency-powered products and services.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="lp__faq">
                    <div class="lp__faq__headline" onclick="window.toggleFaq(this)"><svg width="20" height="20"
                            viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd"
                                d="M20 11.4286H11.4286V20H8.57143V11.4286H0V8.57143H8.57143V0H11.4286V8.57143H20V11.4286Z" />
                        </svg>
                        <h3>What does “Non-custodial” mean?</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="lp__faq__content">
                        <p>It means that the Solflare team has no control over your funds whatsoever. We provide a
                            protocol for you to use - but your funds are yours.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="lp__faq">
                    <div class="lp__faq__headline" onclick="window.toggleFaq(this)"><svg width="20" height="20"
                            viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd"
                                d="M20 11.4286H11.4286V20H8.57143V11.4286H0V8.57143H8.57143V0H11.4286V8.57143H20V11.4286Z" />
                        </svg>
                        <h3>I have an issue - where can I get support?</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="lp__faq__content">
                        <p>The best place to get customer support, ask questions, and hang out with other Solana users
                            is our discord - located <a href="https://discord.com/invite/25ufaEWuMn"
                                target="_blank">here</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="lp__faq">
                    <div class="lp__faq__headline" onclick="window.toggleFaq(this)"><svg width="20" height="20"
                            viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd"
                                d="M20 11.4286H11.4286V20H8.57143V11.4286H0V8.57143H8.57143V0H11.4286V8.57143H20V11.4286Z" />
                        </svg>
                        <h3>Can Solana work with other wallets?</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="lp__faq__content">
                        <p>We're working hard to add support for multiple hardware wallets and CLI generated wallets.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="lp__faq">
                    <div class="lp__faq__headline" onclick="window.toggleFaq(this)"><svg width="20" height="20"
                            viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd"
                                d="M20 11.4286H11.4286V20H8.57143V11.4286H0V8.57143H8.57143V0H11.4286V8.57143H20V11.4286Z" />
                        </svg>
                        <h3>I lost my password? What can I do?</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="lp__faq__content">
                        <p>You can re-import your mnemonic and set a new password.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="lp__faq">
                    <div class="lp__faq__headline" onclick="window.toggleFaq(this)"><svg width="20" height="20"
                            viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd"
                                d="M20 11.4286H11.4286V20H8.57143V11.4286H0V8.57143H8.57143V0H11.4286V8.57143H20V11.4286Z" />
                        </svg>
                        <h3>Does Solana support Ledger Nano X?</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="lp__faq__content">
                        <p>Yes, it does, although we’ve seen some issues with Microsoft devices, so please be advised
                            that Windows users may encounter some problems when connecting to Solana with their Ledger
                            Nano X. This issue has also been acknowledged by Ledger and we’re working on finding a way
                            around it!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="lp__faq">
                    <div class="lp__faq__headline" onclick="window.toggleFaq(this)"><svg width="20" height="20"
                            viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd"
                                d="M20 11.4286H11.4286V20H8.57143V11.4286H0V8.57143H8.57143V0H11.4286V8.57143H20V11.4286Z" />
                        </svg>
                        <h3>How can I unstake my SOL?</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="lp__faq__content">
                        <p>Just click “UNDELEGATE” in the Solana interface and wait for the cooldown period required
                            to make your tokens available for withdrawal. You can use the <a target="_blank"
                                href="https://solanabeach.io">Solana Beach</a> explorer for monitoring the Epochs and
                            check our Solana’s official <a
                                href="https://docs.solana.com/cluster/stake-delegation-and-rewards" target="_blank">docs
                                here</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="lp__faq">
                    <div class="lp__faq__headline" onclick="window.toggleFaq(this)"><svg width="20" height="20"
                            viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd"
                                d="M20 11.4286H11.4286V20H8.57143V11.4286H0V8.57143H8.57143V0H11.4286V8.57143H20V11.4286Z" />
                        </svg>
                        <h3>Can I stake the entire amount that is in my account?</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="lp__faq__content">
                        <p>No. Make sure you account for transaction fees by staking less than the maximum amount
                            available.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
